Tunable.description:
The affordance to test against. For the room the tuned object is in,
if this affordance for the tuned object is the trigger interaction,
the test will pass. Otherwise it will fail.

If checked, this test will return the opposite of what it's tuned to
return. For instance, if "invert" is set and group count is 0,
the test will return true.

TunableVariant.description:
Which screen slam to show when this career level is reached.
Localization Tokens: Sim - {0.SimFirstName}, Level Name - 
{1.String}, Level Number - {2.Number}, Track Name - {3.String}
